# VEHICLE::GET_SUBMARINE_NUMBER_OF_AIR_LEAKS

## Summary
Checks if a Submarine has any air leaks, when there is more than 4 the player will drown

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **INT**
